original_title: Richmond: Romer Road - St. George Road
text:
(1) Romer Road, east side, at St. George Road, showing the residence of Chas. Fay.
August 22, 1925.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) A view northward across the grounds of the Fay residence, toward the house.
August 22, 1925.

P. L. Sperr.
